node.text: From pole to my first DTM win, thank you to the whole team @afcorse_official and @alphatauri!! 😁🏆

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alex Albon on August 22, 2021. May be an image of ‎one or more people, people standing, outdoors and ‎text that says '‎MOOS AUTOHERO ALPHA TAURI ه = ALEK‎'‎‎.
Photo by Alex Albon on August 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bul T Fcorse RACING WITH FERRARI DTM Nürburgring2021 Race8 st Place Driver DTM AUTOHERO AUTO ALPHA TAURI'.
Photo by Alex Albon on August 22, 2021. May be an image of car and road.
Photo shared by Alex Albon on August 05, 2021 tagging @valeyellow46. May be an image of 1 person, child, standing and outdoors.

node.text: I have idolised @valeyellow46 ever since I was a kid. My kart was #46 and covered in Rossi stickers. He’s continued to be one of my biggest inspirations and I will forever admire what he has achieved in motorsport. Congratulations on an incredible career 🙌

node.text: Pace was up there in practice, let’s see what tomorrow’s quali brings ⏳

node.text: Great day testing! Silverstone in an F1 car will always put a smile on my face 😁
